00:06:36.437 --> 00:06:37.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:06:40.108 --> 00:06:44.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Since my Denobulan physiology is immune</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the effects of the disturbance,</i></c.bg_transparent>

109
00:06:44.695 --> 00:06:48.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I volunteered to watch over the crew.</i></c.bg_transparent>

110
00:06:48.866 --> 00:06:52.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>So far... Ah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

111
00:06:52.787 --> 00:06:55.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They've been no trouble at all.</i></c.bg_transparent>

112
00:06:55.706 --> 00:06:58.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>While the computer is controlling</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>most of the ship's systems,</i></c.bg_transparent>

113
00:06:58.709 --> 00:07:01.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I was given a quick tutorial,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>just in case.</i></c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:01.754 --> 00:07:03.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Despite the dire circumstances,</i></c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:03.673 --> 00:07:06.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I must say I relished the challenge...</i></c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:06.676 --> 00:07:10.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>And soon developed a newfound respect</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>for Ensign Mayweather.</i></c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:10.638 --> 00:07:12.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( inaudible )</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:15.726 --> 00:07:18.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: You need to check this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every two hours, minimum.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:18.688 --> 00:07:19.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every two hours.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:20.064 --> 00:07:23.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the impulse manifolds get clogged,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the engines will overload.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:07:23.109 --> 00:07:25.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That would be very bad.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:25.236 --> 00:07:26.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I imagine it would.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:26.654 --> 00:07:27.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No offense, Doc,</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:27.822 --> 00:07:30.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but under normal circumstances,</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:07:30.199 --> 00:07:32.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't even let you in here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without four years</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:34.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of Starfleet training under your belt.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:07:34.454 --> 00:07:36.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>These are hardly normal circumstances.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:07:37.373 --> 00:07:39.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Listen.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:07:39.333 --> 00:07:42.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If something happens,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something you can't handle,</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:07:43.004 --> 00:07:45.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I want you to wake me up.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:07:45.548 --> 00:07:48.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even a few minutes of exposure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would cause permanent damage.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:07:48.468 --> 00:07:50.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it comes down to saving me or the ship?</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:07:52.472 --> 00:07:56.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look. I'm making it easy for you, OK?</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:07.778 --> 00:08:09.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: How's the rest of the crew doing?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:09.405 --> 00:08:12.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sleeping peacefully, except for you.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:12.241 --> 00:08:13.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, lie back.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:13.993 --> 00:08:15.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Doctor--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Ah!</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:15.203 --> 00:08:18.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, Captain, I've told you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the procedure is completely safe.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:18.706 --> 00:08:20.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure it is, but I--</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:08:20.208 --> 00:08:22.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have already had this discussion</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:08:22.710 --> 00:08:24.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with Commander Tucker, Lieutenant Reed,</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:08:24.170 --> 00:08:26.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and virtually</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every other officer on the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:08:26.631 --> 00:08:28.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"I'm not comfortable being incapacitated."</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:08:28.674 --> 00:08:29.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"I really should be at my post."</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:08:29.842 --> 00:08:31.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"I'm willing to risk staying awake."</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:08:31.761 --> 00:08:33.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you can't, nor do you need to.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:08:33.387 --> 00:08:36.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assure you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have everything well in hand.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:08:36.224 --> 00:08:39.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, Doctor. As captain of this ship,</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:08:39.101 --> 00:08:42.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the one who's responsible</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for everyone aboard.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:08:43.189 --> 00:08:44.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's aren't many people</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:08:44.690 --> 00:08:47.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd willingly turn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that responsibility over to.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:08:48.986 --> 00:08:50.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're one of them.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:08:52.573 --> 00:08:54.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah. ( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:08:54.742 --> 00:08:57.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, uh, thank you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:08:57.411 --> 00:09:01.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just wanted to say that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before you put me under.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:19.016 --> 00:09:20.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PHLOX: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>I must say, Dr. Lucas,</i></c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:20.726 --> 00:09:23.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that I appreciated the Captain's</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>vote of confidence.</i></c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:23.187 --> 00:09:26.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I had, in fact,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>been feeling some trepidation</i></c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:26.232 --> 00:09:27.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>over the responsibility I'd been handed.</i></c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:28.025 --> 00:09:33.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>But after two days at the helm,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the ship is running perfectly.</i></c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:33.656 --> 00:09:34.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clatter )</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:09:37.410 --> 00:09:38.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hello?</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:09:45.001 --> 00:09:46.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hello?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:09:53.301 --> 00:09:56.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Nonetheless, I'm not ashamed to admit</i></c.bg_transparent>

165
00:09:56.512 --> 00:10:01.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'll be relieved when</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I can wake up the crew in, uh...</i></c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:05.271 --> 00:10:09.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Two days, 16 hours, and 43 minutes.</i></c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:11.902 --> 00:10:14.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( singing in Denobulan )</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:22.413 --> 00:10:24.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( animals chattering )</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:25.875 --> 00:10:28.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, I know. I'm sorry I'm late.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:43.142 --> 00:10:45.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I don't want the vessel with a pestle.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I want the chalice from the what?</i></c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:45.936 --> 00:10:47.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-The chalice from the palace.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Hmm?</i></c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:47.188 --> 00:10:49.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It's a little crystal chalice</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>with a figure of a palace.</i></c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:49.231 --> 00:10:51.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Does the chalice from the palace</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>have the pellet with the poison?</i></c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:51.233 --> 00:10:53.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>No, the pellet with the poison</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>is in the vessel with a pestle.</i></c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:53.235 --> 00:10:55.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-MAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Oh, the pestle with the vessel.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-WOMAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>The vessel with a pestle.</i></c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:55.237 --> 00:10:56.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>What about the palace</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>from the chalice?</i></c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:56.489 --> 00:10:58.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WOMAN 2: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Not the palace from the chalice.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>The chalice from the palace.</i></c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:58.949 --> 00:11:01.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-MAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Where's the pellet with the poison?</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-WOMAN 2: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>In the vessel with a pestle.</i></c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:01.243 --> 00:11:02.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-WOMAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Don't you see?</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( Porthos whimpers )</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:02.328 --> 00:11:03.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The pellet with the poison's</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>in the vessel with a pestle.</i></c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:03.913 --> 00:11:05.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The chalice from the palace</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>has the brew that is true.</i></c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:05.915 --> 00:11:08.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-So easy, I can say it.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Well, then, you find it.</i></c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:08.125 --> 00:11:09.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Listen carefully.</i></c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:09.710 --> 00:11:10.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( clang )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-The pellet with the poison's</i></c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:10.961 --> 00:11:11.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>in the vessel with a pestle.</i></c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:11.921 --> 00:11:14.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The chalice from the palace</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>has the brew that is true.</i></c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:14.382 --> 00:11:16.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Where the pellet with the poison's</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>in the vessel with a pestle...</i></c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:17.093 --> 00:11:18.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you hear that?</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:18.469 --> 00:11:19.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-WOMAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Good man!</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-WOMAN 2: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Just remember that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:20.012 --> 00:11:22.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Sir Giacomo</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sir Giacomo, into your armor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:22.598 --> 00:11:24.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>And you to your place in the pavilion.</i></c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:27.603 --> 00:11:30.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( clang )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-The pellet with the poison...</i></c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:30.439 --> 00:11:32.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-The pellet with the poison--</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Computer, mute sound.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:32.608 --> 00:11:33.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( inaudible )</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:37.405 --> 00:11:38.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clang )</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:11:41.617 --> 00:11:44.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't sound normal, does it?</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:11:46.789 --> 00:11:49.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose we should investigate, hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:11:58.592 --> 00:11:59.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going alone.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:00.928 --> 00:12:03.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come, Porthos. Come!</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:03.639 --> 00:12:05.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:06.434 --> 00:12:10.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'd be better off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>talking to my Pyrithian bat.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:25.703 --> 00:12:29.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps we were letting our imaginations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>run away with us, hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:29.540 --> 00:12:34.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should never have let Mr. Tucker talk me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into watching </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>The Exorcist </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>last week.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:37.756 --> 00:12:39.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clang )</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:50.978 --> 00:12:52.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hello?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:54.023 --> 00:12:55.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Dr. Phlox.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:58.736 --> 00:13:00.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( Porthos barking )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Porthos!</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:02.698 --> 00:13:04.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Porthos, come back here!</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:05.701 --> 00:13:06.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Porthos!</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:06.785 --> 00:13:08.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gas hissing )</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:17.338 --> 00:13:18.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:13:21.175 --> 00:13:23.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, now don't you feel foolish?</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:13:26.013 --> 00:13:27.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clatter )</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:13:29.391 --> 00:13:30.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:13:32.353 --> 00:13:35.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I called out. Didn't you hear me?</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:13:35.564 --> 00:13:37.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was running a diagnostic.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:13:38.067 --> 00:13:39.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you require my assistance?</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:41.070 --> 00:13:42.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:13:42.821 --> 00:13:45.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I thought it was movie night.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:13:45.407 --> 00:13:47.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could hear that all the way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the mess hall.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:13:47.368 --> 00:13:49.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make a note of it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the maintenance log.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:13:50.746 --> 00:13:51.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:13:51.872 --> 00:13:56.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bangs, squeaks, rattling chains.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:13:58.587 --> 00:14:00.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this a starship or a haunted house?</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:14:01.173 --> 00:14:04.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right, Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You seem somewhat agitated.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:14:04.218 --> 00:14:06.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, considering you nearly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sent me into cardiac shock...</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:14:06.971 --> 00:14:08.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I apologize if I startled you.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:09.640 --> 00:14:11.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're certain that's all?</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:12.434 --> 00:14:16.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I have had a slight headache</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since we entered this region.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:14:16.355 --> 00:14:18.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps Vulcans and Earth canines</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:14:18.357 --> 00:14:21.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>are better able to adapt to it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than Denobulans.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:14:21.610 --> 00:14:25.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you, hmm?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've barely seen you the last two days.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:14:25.114 --> 00:14:27.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've had my duties to attend to.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:14:27.324 --> 00:14:31.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The rest of the time I've spent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my quarters reading, meditating.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:14:31.370 --> 00:14:32.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then you're due for a night out.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:14:32.746 --> 00:14:34.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't you join Porthos and me?</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:14:35.291 --> 00:14:37.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd like to complete the diagnostic.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:14:38.502 --> 00:14:41.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The movie's quite amusing.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:14:41.130 --> 00:14:42.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:14:43.507 --> 00:14:45.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:14:45.175 --> 00:14:47.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I, um, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:14:48.053 --> 00:14:51.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps you'll share a meal with me later.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:14:52.766 --> 00:14:54.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you like.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:14:55.352 --> 00:14:56.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah...</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:15:04.528 --> 00:15:07.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( humming )</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:15:09.033 --> 00:15:11.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:15:13.913 --> 00:15:15.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clattering )</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:15:16.457 --> 00:15:17.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hello?</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:15:24.173 --> 00:15:26.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( humming )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( clatter )</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:15:27.885 --> 00:15:29.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol?</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:15:30.721 --> 00:15:32.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that you?</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:15:45.361 --> 00:15:46.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clatter )</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:47.029 --> 00:15:48.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop!</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:15:51.283 --> 00:15:53.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Phlox to T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

255
00:15:53.702 --> 00:15:55.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would you mind</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>not creeping around the ship</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:15:55.287 --> 00:15:57.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>like a Draxxan cloud viper?</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:15:58.082 --> 00:15:59.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Doctor?</i></c.bg_transparent>

258
00:15:59.291 --> 00:16:03.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please. I wouldn't have imagined</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that Vulcans engaged in childish games.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:03.629 --> 00:16:05.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>I don't understand.</i></c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:05.422 --> 00:16:08.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What were you doing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in engineering just now?</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:08.592 --> 00:16:11.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Doctor, I'm on the bridge.</i></c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:23.232 --> 00:16:25.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah!</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:25.275 --> 00:16:29.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you don't, uh,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mind eating here in the galley.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:29.488 --> 00:16:33.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The mess hall seems a bit, oh, melancholy.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:16:33.784 --> 00:16:35.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All the empty chairs.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:16:35.953 --> 00:16:37.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: This is fine.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:16:37.621 --> 00:16:39.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:16:39.248 --> 00:16:43.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My fifth grandmother made this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for each of my weddings.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:48.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chef's tried to prepare it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he never gets it quite right.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:16:48.382 --> 00:16:51.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( exclaiming )</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:16:52.678 --> 00:16:56.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, his Plomeek broth</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>leaves something to be desired as well.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:16:56.348 --> 00:16:59.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I always thought so,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but, uh, I was afraid to mention it.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:16:59.393 --> 00:17:01.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:17:03.480 --> 00:17:05.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm. ( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:17:05.691 --> 00:17:09.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol, um, you're sure you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>weren't in engineering today?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:17:10.070 --> 00:17:11.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quite sure.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:17:12.906 --> 00:17:14.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What were you doing there?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:17:14.491 --> 00:17:17.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm responsible for</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>monitoring the engines.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:17:17.369 --> 00:17:19.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're supposed to be assisting each other.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:17:19.955 --> 00:17:23.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a large ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for two people to maintain.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:17:24.626 --> 00:17:26.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you have anything to report?</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:17:29.381 --> 00:17:30.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:17:31.550 --> 00:17:33.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could have sworn there was</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone in that room with me.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:17:33.761 --> 00:17:35.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-A member of the crew?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:17:36.055 --> 00:17:39.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everyone except us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is in deep neuro-sedation.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:17:41.393 --> 00:17:44.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then obviously you were mistaken.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:17:44.313 --> 00:17:46.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obviously. ( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:17:47.024 --> 00:17:49.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've never been to Denobula, have you?</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:17:49.526 --> 00:17:51.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:17:51.779 --> 00:17:55.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The cities are quite crowded...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by choice, not by necessity.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:17:55.991 --> 00:17:58.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The atmosphere is vibrant, communal.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:17:58.869 --> 00:18:00.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds fascinating.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:18:00.245 --> 00:18:03.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What I'm saying is that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're a sociable people.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:03.749 --> 00:18:08.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being alone on </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just the two of us,</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:08.587 --> 00:18:11.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has proven more stressful than I imagined.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:18:11.548 --> 00:18:14.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two people aren't even enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a Denobulan marriage--</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:18:14.384 --> 00:18:16.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A proper one, anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:18:16.929 --> 00:18:19.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry I haven't been better company.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:18:19.723 --> 00:18:21.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That isn't what I meant.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:18:21.308 --> 00:18:22.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:18:24.436 --> 00:18:28.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is ironic, however,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I should be your sole companion.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:18:29.066 --> 00:18:33.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unlike your people, most Vulcans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will go to great lengths to find solitude.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:18:34.488 --> 00:18:39.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At times, it has been trying for me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to coexist with 80 humans,</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:18:40.953 --> 00:18:42.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>especially the more irrational ones.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:18:43.622 --> 00:18:46.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm, such as, uh, Commander Tucker.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:18:47.501 --> 00:18:50.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've found the last two days</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be a welcome respite.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:18:51.755 --> 00:18:54.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand, but I, for one,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will never complain again</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:18:54.341 --> 00:18:57.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I can't get a good seat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on movie night.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:19:02.057 --> 00:19:05.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Despite the tragic circumstances</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>surrounding your homecoming, Dr. Lucas,</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:05.602 --> 00:19:07.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you must be happy to return to Earth.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:19:07.437 --> 00:19:08.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:19:10.899 --> 00:19:12.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As I've mentioned before,</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:19:12.234 --> 00:19:16.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no regrets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about accepting my position on </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

314
00:19:16.155 --> 00:19:17.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>However, it has struck me recently</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:19:17.614 --> 00:19:20.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>how much I miss</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the familiar pleasures of my home.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:19:21.076 --> 00:19:22.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:19:26.331 --> 00:19:29.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've experienced the nightclubs</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in our Kaybin district,</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:19:29.585 --> 00:19:34.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so you know the excitement of meeting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a new companion or two,</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:19:34.214 --> 00:19:38.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the intimacy that can develop so quickly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when all parties are receptive.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:19:38.760 --> 00:19:41.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You humans are a truly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>remarkable species, Dr. Lucas,</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:19:41.889 --> 00:19:43.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but when </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has accomplished its mission,</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:19:43.932 --> 00:19:49.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I look forward to being</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>among Denobulans again...</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:19:50.647 --> 00:19:52.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The more of them, the better.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:59.781 --> 00:20:02.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good afternoon, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:20:02.117 --> 00:20:04.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are we feeling today?</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:20:05.913 --> 00:20:09.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah. Neurochemistry looks excellent.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:20:09.249 --> 00:20:11.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Theta waves are good.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:20:11.084 --> 00:20:13.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should wake up extremely well rested.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:20:13.670 --> 00:20:15.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( creaking )</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:20:19.760 --> 00:20:22.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( creaking continues )</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:20:37.444 --> 00:20:39.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:20:40.906 --> 00:20:42.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Phlox to T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:20:44.743 --> 00:20:47.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Internal sensors don't show</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any additional bio-signs.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:20:48.038 --> 00:20:50.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you, it was outside of the ship,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the hull.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:20:50.707 --> 00:20:53.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are no life-forms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anywhere in this vicinity.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:20:53.293 --> 00:20:54.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about alien vessels?</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:20:54.878 --> 00:20:57.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can see for yourself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there's nothing there.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:20:59.675 --> 00:21:02.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said this reconfigured space</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could be affecting our systems.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:21:02.135 --> 00:21:03.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it's interfering with our sensors?</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:21:03.762 --> 00:21:05.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's possible,</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:21:05.222 --> 00:21:07.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we should consider</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another explanation.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:21:08.600 --> 00:21:10.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mentioned you were having difficulty</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:21:10.143 --> 00:21:12.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>adjusting to the solitude</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the past few days.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:21:12.771 --> 00:21:15.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't imagine it! I saw something.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:21:15.774 --> 00:21:18.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Outside the ship, crawling on the hull.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:21:20.529 --> 00:21:22.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about what I saw in engineering?</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:21:22.322 --> 00:21:24.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You ran the scans yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:21:24.491 --> 00:21:26.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is nothing unusual onboard.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:21:32.374 --> 00:21:36.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said you haven't slept much</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since we entered this disturbance.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:21:36.295 --> 00:21:39.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps you should return</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your quarters, try to rest.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:21:43.593 --> 00:21:45.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need to finish my rounds.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:51.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( humming )</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:22:04.656 --> 00:22:05.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get away from her!</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:22:06.033 --> 00:22:07.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:22:17.753 --> 00:22:18.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:22:41.568 --> 00:22:42.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clattering )</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:22:42.778 --> 00:22:43.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:23:00.712 --> 00:23:03.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Phlox to T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Go ahead, Doctor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

359
00:23:03.340 --> 00:23:06.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the Xindi. They're onboard.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:23:08.637 --> 00:23:10.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll need to arm ourselves. I saw two.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:23:10.764 --> 00:23:12.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There could be more of them.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:23:12.099 --> 00:23:13.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing on the sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:23:13.350 --> 00:23:16.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then the sensors must be wrong!</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:23:16.186 --> 00:23:17.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:23:18.438 --> 00:23:19.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Phlox!</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:23:20.357 --> 00:23:22.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought you were going to get some rest.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:23:22.317 --> 00:23:24.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were real! I saw them!</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:23:24.653 --> 00:23:27.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If that's true,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then how did they get on the ship?</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:23:27.656 --> 00:23:28.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah!</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:23:28.824 --> 00:23:31.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All external hatches</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and docking ports are sealed.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:23:31.451 --> 00:23:32.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They could have transporter technology.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:23:33.036 --> 00:23:34.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There were no transporter signatures.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:23:35.038 --> 00:23:37.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What difference does it make</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how they got onboard?</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:23:39.209 --> 00:23:40.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we wake up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant Reed or the Macos,</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:23:41.002 --> 00:23:43.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>they will be incapacitated within minutes,</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:23:43.130 --> 00:23:44.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>dead within hours.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:23:44.422 --> 00:23:46.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is up to us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to deal with this situation.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:23:50.220 --> 00:23:52.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I plan to start on "G" deck</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and work my way up.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:23:52.222 --> 00:23:54.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to stop them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>whether you help me or not.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:24:16.538 --> 00:24:18.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:25:06.004 --> 00:25:07.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've searched four decks.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:25:07.839 --> 00:25:09.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That leaves three to go.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:25:09.925 --> 00:25:13.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there are Xindi aboard,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why are they concealing themselves?</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:25:13.887 --> 00:25:16.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They could be trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

385
00:25:16.139 --> 00:25:18.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What better time than while</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the crew is incapacitated?</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:25:18.099 --> 00:25:20.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:25:20.393 --> 00:25:21.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A bio-sign.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:25:21.686 --> 00:25:25.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are over 80 bio-signs aboard,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>not counting your pets in sick bay.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:25:25.482 --> 00:25:27.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't human.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:25:27.150 --> 00:25:28.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither are your pets.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:25:28.985 --> 00:25:31.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah. I can't lock onto it.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:25:31.154 --> 00:25:35.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There must be some interference,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>possibly from the reconfigured space.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:25:35.325 --> 00:25:36.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said it wasn't affecting our sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:25:36.993 --> 00:25:38.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I said it wasn't affecting main sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:25:38.995 --> 00:25:41.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That hand scanner is far less powerful.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:25:41.998 --> 00:25:44.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have it.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:25:56.054 --> 00:25:57.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's just ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:26:00.517 --> 00:26:03.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clicking )</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:26:11.987 --> 00:26:13.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor!</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:26:17.951 --> 00:26:19.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whimpers )</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:26:19.661 --> 00:26:20.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:26:21.788 --> 00:26:25.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fortunately, I'm not very proficient</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with hand weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:26:25.125 --> 00:26:27.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did he get out?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:26:27.294 --> 00:26:30.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... I believe I, um...</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:26:30.088 --> 00:26:31.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We went for a walk earlier.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:26:31.381 --> 00:26:34.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I might have neglected to put him back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:26:34.843 --> 00:26:36.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you simply forgot?</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:26:36.594 --> 00:26:38.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been distracted!</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:26:38.388 --> 00:26:39.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would've thought this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could tell the difference</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:26:39.764 --> 00:26:41.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>between a giant insect and a beagle!</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:26:41.891 --> 00:26:45.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It can, if you use it properly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You're the science officer!</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:26:45.478 --> 00:26:47.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You might have offered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some assistance in that area.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:26:47.314 --> 00:26:49.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You feel I haven't been helpful?</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:26:49.983 --> 00:26:52.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How would you characterize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the two hours I wasted</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:26:52.110 --> 00:26:54.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>searching for a figment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your imagination?</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:26:54.362 --> 00:26:56.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm not delusional!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you certain?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:26:56.906 --> 00:26:58.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As I recall, you once told Ensign Sato</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:26:59.034 --> 00:27:02.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that it's considered healthy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Denobulans to hallucinate.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:27:02.912 --> 00:27:04.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's how you release stress.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:27:04.414 --> 00:27:07.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been under a lot of stress lately,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>haven't you, Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:27:08.626 --> 00:27:09.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not unheard of, but I--</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:27:10.045 --> 00:27:11.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said you've been having headaches.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:27:12.714 --> 00:27:15.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there anything else</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you care to tell me?</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:27:15.133 --> 00:27:16.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine!</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:27:16.217 --> 00:27:17.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You nearly shot the Captain's dog!</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:27:17.844 --> 00:27:21.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to recalibrate this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to exclude canine bio-signs,</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:27:21.139 --> 00:27:23.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and then I'm going to finish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>searching this ship.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:27:23.641 --> 00:27:26.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am not seeing things,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I intend to prove it!</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:27:34.069 --> 00:27:35.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:27:35.153 --> 00:27:37.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign Sato to the doctor!</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:27:41.242 --> 00:27:42.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hoshi?</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:27:43.787 --> 00:27:45.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hoshi?</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:27:49.834 --> 00:27:51.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( water running )</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:27:54.255 --> 00:27:55.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:28:04.682 --> 00:28:06.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hoshi?</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:28:08.645 --> 00:28:10.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:28:10.480 --> 00:28:12.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to put you back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>under sedation immediately!</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:28:12.399 --> 00:28:14.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll suffer permanent damage.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:28:16.736 --> 00:28:18.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hoshi.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:28:19.155 --> 00:28:20.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did this.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:28:21.116 --> 00:28:22.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:28:22.826 --> 00:28:24.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said we'd be safe.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:28:25.620 --> 00:28:26.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me get you to sick bay.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:28:26.913 --> 00:28:28.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You promised us!</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:29:00.196 --> 00:29:01.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol...</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:29:03.032 --> 00:29:05.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please meet me in sick bay immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:29:19.215 --> 00:29:20.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where have you been? I was calling you.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:29:20.884 --> 00:29:22.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:29:22.302 --> 00:29:25.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain... W-what are you doing up?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:29:25.472 --> 00:29:26.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol woke me.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:29:26.973 --> 00:29:29.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She said something was wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:29:29.392 --> 00:29:30.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what's happening.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:29:31.227 --> 00:29:33.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She said you've been seeing things,</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:29:33.104 --> 00:29:35.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>something about Xindi onboard the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:29:38.026 --> 00:29:39.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not concerned about that?</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:29:40.653 --> 00:29:42.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm more concerned about you.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:29:42.155 --> 00:29:44.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I obviously expected too much from you.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:29:44.365 --> 00:29:45.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not real.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:29:45.992 --> 00:29:47.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't you go to your quarters?</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:29:47.577 --> 00:29:50.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lie down. I'll take over.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:29:50.246 --> 00:29:51.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did the best you could.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:29:51.498 --> 00:29:53.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You are not real!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:29:53.374 --> 00:29:55.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:30:07.555 --> 00:30:09.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was so busy monitoring the crew,</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:30:09.224 --> 00:30:12.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never thought to run</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another neural scan on myself.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:30:15.355 --> 00:30:17.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The effects are subtle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and difficult to detect,</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:30:18.024 --> 00:30:22.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but there are disruptions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>deep within my neocortex.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:30:24.823 --> 00:30:26.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were right.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:30:27.116 --> 00:30:29.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hallucinating.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:30:32.539 --> 00:30:34.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you in danger?</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:35.041 --> 00:30:37.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't believe there'll be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any permanent damage.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:39.087 --> 00:30:40.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>However, it's obviously</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>affecting my judgment.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:30:40.880 --> 00:30:44.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no choice but to put myself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>under neuro-sedation</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:30:44.968 --> 00:30:48.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and ask you to look after the crew.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:30:50.223 --> 00:30:52.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have the medical expertise.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:30:52.475 --> 00:30:54.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With your scientific background,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you should have no problems.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:30:54.644 --> 00:30:55.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have my own duties.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:30:55.979 --> 00:30:58.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't possibly monitor the entire crew.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:30:59.023 --> 00:30:59.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't be for long.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:31:00.024 --> 00:31:02.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be coming out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the disturbance in less than six hours.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:31:03.486 --> 00:31:05.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol, I'm asking for your help.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:31:05.321 --> 00:31:06.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:31:06.656 --> 00:31:07.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why not?</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:31:10.159 --> 00:31:14.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When we were searching the ship,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I... became irritated with you.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:31:14.539 --> 00:31:15.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apparently I deserved it.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:31:16.082 --> 00:31:17.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:31:19.002 --> 00:31:22.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was on the verge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of losing control of my emotions.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:31:24.674 --> 00:31:27.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This reconfigured space</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is affecting me as well.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:31:28.678 --> 00:31:30.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why didn't you tell me?</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:31:30.305 --> 00:31:32.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd hoped to control it,</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:31:32.098 --> 00:31:34.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it's proven more difficult</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than I thought.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:31:34.767 --> 00:31:37.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The crew is better off in your hands.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:31:39.522 --> 00:31:41.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt that.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:31:41.524 --> 00:31:43.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I nearly killed Porthos, remember?</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:31:43.610 --> 00:31:45.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if one of these delusions causes me</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:31:45.111 --> 00:31:47.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to open an airlock</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or shut down life support?</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:31:47.405 --> 00:31:50.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You won't do that.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How do you know?</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:31:50.700 --> 00:31:55.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because your duty is to look out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the welfare of this crew.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:31:55.538 --> 00:31:57.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do you think the Captain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>allowed you to sedate him</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:31:58.082 --> 00:32:00.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>over Commander Tucker's objections?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:32:00.960 --> 00:32:04.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because he trusts you, as do I.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:32:06.507 --> 00:32:08.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure I trust myself.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:32:08.593 --> 00:32:11.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just a few more hours, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:32:15.475 --> 00:32:16.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PHLOX: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>So, Dr. Lucas, </i></c.bg_transparent>

505
00:32:16.684 --> 00:32:18.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>while the past few days</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>have proven challenging,</i></c.bg_transparent>

506
00:32:18.978 --> 00:32:24.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>both T'Pol and I are relieved</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>that our adventure is nearly over. </i></c.bg_transparent>

507
00:32:24.317 --> 00:32:26.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once we've confirmed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're out of the disturbance,</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:32:26.694 --> 00:32:29.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can begin waking the senior officers.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:32:29.489 --> 00:32:32.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My medical staff should be next.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:32:32.116 --> 00:32:34.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They can assist me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the rest of the, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:32:36.037 --> 00:32:38.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, we should have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of the disturbance half an hour ago.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:32:40.750 --> 00:32:44.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There could have been some slight</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>navigational discrepancies.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:32:44.170 --> 00:32:46.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought space travel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was supposed to be precise.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:32:46.756 --> 00:32:48.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not always. Check long-range sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:32:48.675 --> 00:32:50.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you think I'm doing?</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:32:53.221 --> 00:32:54.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's more than a slight discrepancy.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:32:54.889 --> 00:32:56.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This can't be correct.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:32:57.266 --> 00:32:59.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're nearly a quarter of</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a light-year from the far edge.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:32:59.394 --> 00:33:00.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At our current rate of speed,</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:33:00.812 --> 00:33:03.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we won't be out of this for another...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>10 weeks!</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:33:14.575 --> 00:33:16.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Auto-navigation is still engaged.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:33:16.160 --> 00:33:18.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Engines are online. Why aren't we through?</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:33:18.121 --> 00:33:19.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The reconfigured space has expanded.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:33:19.831 --> 00:33:21.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But we knew it would!</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:33:21.165 --> 00:33:23.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Travis said our course</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and speed would compensate.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:33:25.336 --> 00:33:26.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol?</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:33:27.296 --> 00:33:29.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obviously the rate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of expansion has accelerated.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:33:29.966 --> 00:33:31.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need to increase speed.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:33:31.801 --> 00:33:33.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're already at full impulse.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:33.386 --> 00:33:34.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As you can see, that's insufficient.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:34.679 --> 00:33:35.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need to go to warp.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:36.389 --> 00:33:37.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Tucker said</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it would be too dangerous.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:33:37.765 --> 00:33:39.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't know what might happen.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:33:39.100 --> 00:33:40.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you propose?</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:33:40.601 --> 00:33:43.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keeping the crew comatose</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the next 10 weeks?</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:33:46.065 --> 00:33:48.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PHLOX: All right. What do we do first?</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:48.735 --> 00:33:51.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( voice breaking ) I'm afraid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I may not be of much assistance.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:51.529 --> 00:33:53.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do I need to keep reminding you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you are the science officer?</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:33:53.865 --> 00:33:56.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I already told you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm finding it difficult to focus.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:33:56.492 --> 00:34:00.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>On your worst day, you're more qualified</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to operate the warp engines than I am.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:34:00.121 --> 00:34:03.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unfortunately, this is by far</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one of my worst days.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:34:03.541 --> 00:34:05.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a physician, not an engineer!</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:34:05.793 --> 00:34:07.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You hold a dozen scientific degrees.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:34:07.879 --> 00:34:09.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>None of them are in warp theory!</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:34:09.505 --> 00:34:11.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:34:11.924 --> 00:34:15.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The procedures for restarting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the reactor are in the database.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:34:16.512 --> 00:34:19.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you suggesting I read the manual?</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:34:23.936 --> 00:34:28.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Output must be confined</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to within 300 and 312 millicochranes</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:28.900 --> 00:34:31.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to prevent fusion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the dilithium matrix."</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:31.819 --> 00:34:33.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That seems simple enough.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:36.032 --> 00:34:40.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Unless the spatial-compression index</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is greater than 5.62%</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:34:40.536 --> 00:34:43.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or the ship is within two parsecs</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:34:43.331 --> 00:34:47.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of a class-C</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gravimetric field distortion"?</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:34:47.210 --> 00:34:49.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I realize this is a complex procedure.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:34:49.420 --> 00:34:51.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Complex? This is utterly baffling.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:34:51.589 --> 00:34:53.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It might as well be written</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in ancient Klingon,</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:34:53.382 --> 00:34:56.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for all the sense I can make of it.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:34:56.135 --> 00:34:57.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:34:58.763 --> 00:35:00.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:35:00.223 --> 00:35:04.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I just wish I could be more helpful.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:35:04.352 --> 00:35:06.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're doing fine.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:35:06.562 --> 00:35:09.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have to close the plasma relays</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before we can begin the startup sequence.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:35:09.774 --> 00:35:11.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would you mind?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:35:13.653 --> 00:35:15.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What the hell are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:35:15.905 --> 00:35:18.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you not to mess</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the warp engines.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:35:18.658 --> 00:35:20.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have time for this.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:35:20.159 --> 00:35:21.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You better make time, Doc.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:35:22.036 --> 00:35:26.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you, you can't start</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the warp reactor inside this disturbance.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:35:26.124 --> 00:35:28.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, you told me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it would be difficult, not impossible.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:35:28.376 --> 00:35:30.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That machine was designed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to manipulate space,</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:35:30.837 --> 00:35:32.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to violate the laws of motion.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:35:33.047 --> 00:35:35.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You make the tiniest mistake,</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:35:35.091 --> 00:35:37.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you'll collapse the warp field,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll crush this ship.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:35:37.343 --> 00:35:38.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you for the warning.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:35:38.719 --> 00:35:40.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're gonna screw this up, Phlox.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:35:40.138 --> 00:35:41.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Go away!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You're gonna kill everybody!</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:35:41.806 --> 00:35:42.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can't you see I'm busy?</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:35:43.015 --> 00:35:45.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor! Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:35:48.604 --> 00:35:50.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:35:50.148 --> 00:35:51.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:35:51.983 --> 00:35:54.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't find the plasma relays.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:35:56.195 --> 00:35:57.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do it myself.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:36:01.200 --> 00:36:03.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deuterium pressure is nominal.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:36:03.953 --> 00:36:07.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Antimatter constrictor coils are online.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:36:07.123 --> 00:36:09.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Warp 2, hmm, should be sufficient?</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:36:09.125 --> 00:36:10.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shall we try?</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:36:16.674 --> 00:36:18.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The intermix is stable.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:36:20.469 --> 00:36:22.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A warp field is forming. ( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:36:22.722 --> 00:36:25.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What's wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:36:25.349 --> 00:36:27.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I-I-I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:36:37.320 --> 00:36:39.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I followed the procedures exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:36:39.822 --> 00:36:41.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What did I do wrong?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You need to--</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:36:41.991 --> 00:36:43.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:36:43.492 --> 00:36:45.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What, T'Pol? Help me!</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:36:45.203 --> 00:36:48.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( stammering )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Is it... The particle confinement?</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:36:48.247 --> 00:36:49.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps you should increase it.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:36:49.790 --> 00:36:51.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, how do I do that?</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:36:52.543 --> 00:36:54.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:36:57.006 --> 00:36:59.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Particle confinement.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:36:59.175 --> 00:37:01.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Particle confinement!</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:37:03.429 --> 00:37:06.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor... Perhaps we should</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wake Commander Tucker.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:37:06.974 --> 00:37:08.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll die.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:37:08.476 --> 00:37:10.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we destroy the ship, we'll all die.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:37:10.394 --> 00:37:12.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:37:13.731 --> 00:37:18.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we can't accomplish our mission,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>billions of people on Earth could die.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:37:18.361 --> 00:37:22.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isn't it logical to sacrifice one life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to save so many?</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:37:22.657 --> 00:37:24.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to make that sacrifice yet!</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:37:27.328 --> 00:37:28.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Particle confinement!</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:37:30.873 --> 00:37:33.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Increase power to magnetic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>constriction coils!</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:37:41.092 --> 00:37:42.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol!</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:37:42.510 --> 00:37:43.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, here!</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:37:50.559 --> 00:37:52.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling stops )</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:37:52.103 --> 00:37:53.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The field is stabilizing.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:37:55.898 --> 00:37:57.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's holding.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:37:57.358 --> 00:37:58.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I suggest we go to warp.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:38:00.027 --> 00:38:01.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Engaging warp engines.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:38:12.748 --> 00:38:13.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Warp 1.1.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:38:15.876 --> 00:38:17.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>1.2.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:38:17.545 --> 00:38:20.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whooshing )</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:38:20.172 --> 00:38:22.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pressure on the hull's increasing.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:38:24.176 --> 00:38:25.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:38:25.386 --> 00:38:27.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant Reed insisted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on showing me how to transfer</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:38:27.555 --> 00:38:29.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>power to the hull plating...</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:38:29.348 --> 00:38:31.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just in case.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:38:35.980 --> 00:38:38.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems to be working.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:38:38.274 --> 00:38:40.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Warp 1.8.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:38:40.276 --> 00:38:41.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>1.9.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:38:43.070 --> 00:38:45.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Warp 2! ( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:39:08.554 --> 00:39:10.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:39:10.723 --> 00:39:13.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, ah, ah! Lie still.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:39:13.142 --> 00:39:15.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your neocortex may need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a few moments to warm up.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:39:18.773 --> 00:39:21.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are we th-through the disturbance?</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:39:21.442 --> 00:39:25.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes. I'll begin waking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the rest of the crew shortly.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:39:25.821 --> 00:39:27.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any...problems?</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:39:29.158 --> 00:39:33.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, a few minor glitches.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It will all be in my log.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:39:33.621 --> 00:39:34.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:39:34.705 --> 00:39:37.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're feeling up to it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you have a visitor.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:39:39.668 --> 00:39:41.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, hey.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:39:44.799 --> 00:39:46.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:39:48.511 --> 00:39:50.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:39:50.096 --> 00:39:52.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-A little woozy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm not surprised.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:39:52.306 --> 00:39:54.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You haven't eaten anything in four days.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:39:54.725 --> 00:39:56.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get to the mess hall.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:39:56.352 --> 00:39:58.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, aye, Doc.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:40:03.192 --> 00:40:05.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll assist you in waking the others.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, that won't be necessary.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:40:06.028 --> 00:40:09.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate the offer,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but, uh, you need some rest.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:40:09.365 --> 00:40:11.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me walk you to your quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:40:11.534 --> 00:40:14.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Doctor's orders?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:40:21.419 --> 00:40:22.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:40:24.088 --> 00:40:27.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll stop by and check on you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a few hours.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:40:49.238 --> 00:40:51.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PHLOX: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>As you might guess, Dr. Lucas,</i></c.bg_transparent>

652
00:40:51.282 --> 00:40:54.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I had considered deleting this letter</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and starting over,</i></c.bg_transparent>

653
00:40:54.660 --> 00:40:57.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>since large sections of it</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>are now obviously fictitious.</i></c.bg_transparent>

654
00:40:57.496 --> 00:41:00.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>However, I decided that</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>my delusional account</i></c.bg_transparent>

655
00:41:00.249 --> 00:41:02.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>would probably prove entertaining.</i></c.bg_transparent>

656
00:41:02.084 --> 00:41:04.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>As always, you have my best wishes.</i></c.bg_transparent>

657
00:41:04.670 --> 00:41:08.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Your friend and colleague, Phlox.</i></c.bg_transparent>

658
00:41:08.466 --> 00:41:10.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I join you?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:41:10.426 --> 00:41:11.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:41:13.012 --> 00:41:14.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:41:15.514 --> 00:41:16.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Tucker was complaining</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:41:16.724 --> 00:41:19.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that it will take him days</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to realign the warp coils.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:41:19.852 --> 00:41:21.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:41:21.687 --> 00:41:23.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, he gave me quite a talking to.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:41:24.273 --> 00:41:26.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He also said, and I quote,</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:41:26.901 --> 00:41:28.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Phlox did one hell of a job."</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:41:30.446 --> 00:41:32.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: Oh. Excuse me, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:41:35.117 --> 00:41:37.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must have enjoyed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>having the ship to yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:41:38.871 --> 00:41:41.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't nearly as empty</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as I anticipated.</c.bg_transparent>

